{"tid":1245604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【郊外野餐冇signal？】請大家下載定Open Street Map，以防冇信號後唔識地形","createTime":"2019-06-20T11:18:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T16:24:43.000Z","uid":131691,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b6a5c964a0492812626611af62a13004f22c23bb","tid":1245604,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T11:18:14.000Z","msg":"OsmAnd係一個based on Open Street Map嘅app，佢嘅好處係可以事先下載成個地區嘅地圖，冇信號嘅時候都可以用。<br />\n若果香港人去到山卡罅嘅偏僻地方，驚會冇信號，呢個app可以幫到你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nAndroid（Google Play版）: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=net.osmand&amp;referrer=utm_source%3Dwebsite%26utm_medium%3Dtop\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dnet.osmand%26referrer%3Dutm_source%253Dwebsite%2526utm_medium%253Dtop&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D3hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=439e6d50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=net.osmand&amp;referrer=utm_source%3Dwebsite%26utm_medium%3Dtop</a><br />\nAndroid（F-Droid版，功能完全unlock）: <a href=\"https://f-droid.org/en/packages/net.osmand.plus/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ff-droid.org%2Fen%2Fpackages%2Fnet.osmand.plus%2F&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D3hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=34162ba5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://f-droid.org/en/packages/net.osmand.plus/</a><br />\niOS: <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/app/id934850257\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fapp%2Fid934850257&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D3hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=8d46796a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/app/id934850257</a><br />\n網頁版: <a href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.openstreetmap.org%2F&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D3hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=14171196\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.openstreetmap.org/</a><br />\n<br />\n安裝後記得下載「亞洲 &gt; 香港地區」嘅地圖。<br />\nOpen Street Map嘅地圖數據係民間自發咁用GPS量度跟住upload，所以有時會比Google Maps更詳盡。<br />\n==比較==<br />\nGoogle Maps 金鐘：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J7FpW6H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ7FpW6H.png&h=1c40c709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nOpen Street Map 金鐘：<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/seadQrM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FseadQrM.png&h=c41057d1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n============<br />\nGoogle Maps 中環：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pXJu8dU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpXJu8dU.png&h=a389a579&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nOpen Street Map 中環：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4J2vSFH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4J2vSFH.png&h=f6dd2e51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nOpen Street Map 中環，開啓transport layer專睇運輸路線：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5kaJtev.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5kaJtev.png&h=ea15ebf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nOpen Street Map 中環，開啓humanitarian layer專畀人道救援人士用：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5DPx51e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5DPx51e.png&h=2d63b7aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"349c1bbbff61b350f18a652f377d9df297363639","tid":1245604,"uid":130339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T11:20:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fb7b1f2cf0c21bf68a9251a0a63a8ce9b221edb3","tid":1245604,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T11:20:22.000Z","msg":"希望大家有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8afd3701fa14956bae92439fd233b3c39767033","tid":1245604,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T11:31:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c815f79fdeacf5ed13d2ae1077ddc